user.biography:
Just a spunky 2 year old partially blind rescue pup who looks a bit like a Picasso masterpiece!🥴
Adopted from @omkshelter & so loved💙
Brodie stuff!👇😊

node.text: Brodie found one of the last snow piles that hasn’t melted yet, and he had a blast sliding down it and pouncing into the hole he dug! He never ceases to amaze us with the cute things he does 😂❤️ check out the full IGTV video to see the rest of his antics!

node.text:
Check out Brodie’s new @barkbadge! This pet tag has a QR code that can be scanned with any phone and will instantly bring you to a complete profile of your fur baby. 🐶💖 This can be very handy if they ever get lost! 🥺

When someone scans the @barkbadge tag they can see info about your pets personality, their name, any allergies, and most importantly they can call or email you directly to notify you that your little buddy has been found! Best of all you don’t need an app, a subscription or batteries to use @barkbadge. It’s so simple to set up. You can never be too careful when it comes to your beloved furry family member!🙌🏼😊 Use the code “brodie15” and receive 15% off! Link in bio! #barkbadge

Congratulations to the 1st place winner @ketchupthecavoodle, 2nd place @sargeandleo, and last but not least, @10jamiszelc03 in 3rd!!! We hope you all enjoy your prizes and love your new @stylish.hound gear!!! 😆💖

node.text: We keep Brodie healthy with daily supplements from @controlledlabs_pets! The trio pack we use includes Orange TRIad, Orange Oximega Fish Oil, and Orange Allergy Immune. Head to the link in our bio and use code BRODIE for 30% off your entire order!! Unlike most pet supplements, your pooch will absolutely love these!! 🤗❤️ #controlledlabspets

node.text: Hey guys! Just wanted to remind you all to enter the @stylish.hound giveaway on our previous reel post! There are 3 prizes up for grabs including a $300, $200, and $100 voucher for their website! All of the awesome items in this photo plus even more are available to purchase with the winning vouchers!! Can’t wait to announce the winners and give a few of you the chance to get your hands on some pet products we absolutely LOVE! 🤗❤️😄 Good luck!!!

✨GIVEAWAY✨ We’ve teamed up with @stylish.hound, one of our FAVE brands, to give away three awesome prizes!!! All of the goodies in this video are some of the amazing products you’ll be able to choose from. Sorry, Brodie is not included! 🤣

To enter: 
Follow @stylish.hound and @bestboybrodie (we check😏)
Tag a minimum of three friends! Extra tags mean extra entries! 🤗
For a bonus entry, share this post to your stories!!!

The winners will receive:
1st prize: $300 voucher💖
2nd prize: $200 voucher 💜
3rd prize: $100 voucher 💙

This contest is open internationally, the vouchers will be in $AU, and they can be used to purchase anything on @stylish.hound’s website! Winners will be chosen and announced next week! Good luck!!! 🥰❤️🤗 #stylishhound #giveaway

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Brodie on July 14, 2021 tagging @dogsofinstagram, @instagram, @weratedogs, and @pawsup. May be an image of dog and grass.

node.text: Hey everyone!!! We haven’t posted for a while because we went to British Columbia for our vacation, but we’re back now feeling fresh and rejuvenated! Prepare for your daily dose of Brodie to start again lol 😏😋. Hope you’re all having an amazing summer so far!!! ❤️😍🥰

node.text: Beach days with Brodie are so much fun! 🏖 He tried his absolute best to get that soggy bread out of the water 😅. Sometimes it’s better to let him challenge himself in situations like this, and he always ends up figuring it out like the smart boy he is!! 🤗
